title: Over 300 Ontario Canada ghost towns (maps, pics, directions)
description:
Ontario Ghost Towns 
volume 1

Published by Muskoka Software Group

This CD collection of over 3oo ghost towns located in Ontario, Canada
was cracked by Ziggy Stardust. It used simple checksum protection for
the serial number check.

Now you can explore over 300 locations located in Ontario, Canada
using your browser and a map.
